      "content": "it didn't feel like a coincidence though. it felt... scripted. like the system just reused an asset to save on processing. i've been noticing other things too, like how some people seem to have no depth or repeating dialogue in casual convo. if this is a simulation hitting its limits, how would i even verify it? like what kind of things should i be looking for to prove the environment is looping?",
